name: El mago
description: The magician (Tarot) is set in motion by assuming his own existence. It is the encounter with internal unity, the recognition of potentialities and the sense of vital objectives, which transforms into action, to activate the power to heal reality and take a different place in front of it. Analog inking and pointillism, with digital painting. 2228x1402px, 300dpi and 2.94mb.
